      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped onion </strong>and<strong> diced red pepper</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4 min or until softened</p>",
